258
00:16:33,911 --> 00:16:35,245
You were thinking about sex.

259
00:16:37,206 --> 00:16:38,206
Psh, no.

260
00:16:38,207 --> 00:16:40,291
Yes, you were.
Specifically about shagging me.

261
00:16:40,292 --> 00:16:42,127
