264
00:16:50,469 --> 00:16:52,054
No! Fucking stand over there!

265
00:16:55,182 --> 00:16:56,182
Over there!

266
00:16:57,142 --> 00:16:58,352
Nowhere fucking near me.

267
00:16:59,228 --> 00:17:00,395
